Nigerian disc jockey, Florence Otedola popularly known as Cuppy, has revealed why she remained friends with her former boyfriend, Victor Anichebe. She disclosed this on Saturday via her Twitter account, stating that the Nigerian footballer and her chose peace and positivity over strife despite not being together. Cuppy further expressed that being great people doesn’t mean you’re compatible as a couple. She wrote, “Just got off the phone with my ex boyfriend Victor Anichebe . “I LOVE our friendship! It took us a WHILE to get here it’s about realising life is too short for beef. We choose peace + positivity! “Just because you’re two great people doesn’t mean you’re compatible as a couple.”